data.yaml:
global:
  scrape_interval: 5s
  scrape_timeout: 5s
  scrape_protocols:
  - OpenMetricsText1.0.0
  - OpenMetricsText0.0.1
  - PrometheusText1.0.0
  - PrometheusText0.0.4
  evaluation_interval: 1m
  metric_name_validation_scheme: utf8
runtime:
  gogc: 75
alerting:
  alertmanagers:
  - follow_redirects: true
    enable_http2: true
    scheme: http
    timeout: 10s
    api_version: v2
    static_configs:
    - targets:
      - alertmanager:9093
rule_files:
- /etc/prometheus/prometheus_rules.yml
otlp:
  translation_strategy: UnderscoreEscapingWithSuffixes
